==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: liè bì qūzhú liáng bì
===Etymology===
Literally: The bad coins drive out the good coins.
===Proverb===
'''[[劣]][[币]][[驱逐]][[良]][[币]]'''
# Mediocre talent will drive away people of real talent.
===Alternate forms===
*[[劣幣驅逐良幣]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

